If you choose not to import all feats earned across multiple save files, only the feats marked as unlocked in your most recently loaded save will carry over to your next playthrough. Keep this in mind if you are aiming for 100% completion!

Spending coins on feat boosters does not permanently use up your coins, and coins earned from a feat cannot be earned a second time. Any spent coins will remain in your personal bank of coins and will be available the next time you start a new game.

Changing settings in specific ways may prevent you from earning some feats, and coins, in your current game. Enabling cheats at any point will prevent you from earning feats for the remainder of your current playthrough. You will be warned if you are about to change any setting that does this.
Some feats display as earned as soon as you meet the requirements, while others won't trigger until the next in-game hour. Happy hunting!

As you play through Degrees of Lewdity, you will obtain feats by completing different tasks. The more feats you earn, the more VrelCoins you will earn. When you start a new game, the coins associated with your most recently loaded save can be used to purchase feat boosters. These boosters grant you bonuses in your next game.

Feats are earned linearly over the course of a single playthrough. If you load an earlier save or switch to a different playthrough, you will lose the feat and its VrelCoins, unless you import all of your feats using the link below. This will reset all feat boosters.
